query: SELECT DISTINCT t.id as turmaId, t.codigo as turmaCodigo, e.tipoEvento FROM turmas t INNER JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id INNER JOIN briefing_grupo bg ON bg.eventoId = e.id ORDER BY t.codigo, e.tipoEvento;
